text: Alphonsea hainanensis is a species of plant in the Annonaceae family. It has been recorded from Vietnam and China. ==References== * China Plant Specialist Group 2004. Alphonsea hainanensis. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 20 August 2007.
